S_n\to 0 \iff|S_n|\to 0
 \begin{align} \lim\limits_{n\to\infty}S_n=0&\Longleftrightarrow (\forall\varepsilon>0\quad\exists N\in\mathbb{N}\quad\forall n>N\implies|S_n-0|\leq\varepsilon)\\ &\Longleftrightarrow (\forall\varepsilon>0\quad\exists N\in\mathbb{N}\quad\forall n>N\implies||S_n|-0|\leq\varepsilon) \Longleftrightarrow\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}|S_n|=0\end{align} 
